---
import BasicLayout from "../layouts/BasicLayout.astro";
import GitLogo from "../assets/logo-github.svg";
import LinkedInLogo from "../assets/logo-linkedin.svg";
---

<BasicLayout title="Home">
  <div
    class="home text-secondary m-1 flex flex-col gap-4 border-1 border-gray-700 p-2 lg:w-5"
  >
    <section class="home__start decoration-grey-500 flex flex-col gap-4 p-1">
      <h1 class="decoration-tertiary text-2xl font-bold underline decoration-4">
        Hi, I'm Paulina üëã
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500">
        Astro is a modern static site generator optimized websites with ease. It
        leverages the power of JavaScript frameworks like React, Vue, and
        Svelte, while keeping the final output minimal and efficient. Whether
        you're building a blog, portfolio, or e-commerce site, Astro provides
        the flexibility.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-500">
        Discover the power of Astro, a modern static site generator that
        combines the best of JavaScript frameworks with minimal, optimized
        output for exceptional performance and flexibility.
      </p>
      <ul class="home__start--icon flex gap-4">
        <li class="icon rounded border-1 border-gray-700 p-2">
          <GitLogo size={30} mode="sprite" />
        </li>
        <li class="icon rounded border-1 border-gray-700 p-2">
          <LinkedInLogo size={30} mode="sprite" />
